c: 59
v: 14
t: Iwo sadzamenyana nawe ngati gulu limodzi ayi koma mozemba pogwiritsa ntchito Malinga ya m’mizinda kapena pobisala kuzipupa. Mtima womenya nkhondo ulipo pakati pawo moti iwe ukhoza kuganiza kuti ndi ogwirizana. Koma mitima yawo ndi yogawikana chifukwa iwo ndi anthu osadziwa chilichonse